---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Mitchell Schauer | Systems Integration Architect">
  
  <nav class="fixed top-0 w-full z-50 bg-black/80 backdrop-blur-md border-b border-gray-800">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-4 flex justify-between items-center">
      <span class="font-mono text-blue-400 font-bold tracking-tighter text-xl">MS.ARCHITECT</span>
      <div class="hidden md:flex gap-8 text-sm font-mono text-gray-400">
        <a href="#infrastructure" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">/Infrastructure</a>
        <a href="#industrial" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">/Industrial</a>
        <a href="#research" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">/Research</a>
        <a href="#contact" class="hover:text-teal-400 transition-colors">/Connect</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <main class="pt-32">
    <section class="px-6 max-w-7xl mx-auto mb-32">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div>
          <h1 class="text-7xl font-extrabold text-white leading-none mb-8">
            Systems <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-teal-400">Integration</span> Architect
          </h1>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-8">
            Specializing in the convergence of industrial hardware and modern secure infrastructure. I bridge legacy systems with edge-intelligence to create high-velocity production ecosystems.
          </p>
          <div class="flex gap-4">
             <a href="/resume.pdf" class="bg-white text-black px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-bold hover:bg-blue-500 hover:text-white transition-all">Download Dossier</a>
             <a href="https://github.com/mitchschauer" class="border border-gray-700 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-bold hover:bg-gray-800 transition-all">Source Code</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="absolute -inset-4 bg-blue-500/10 blur-3xl rounded-full"></div>
          <div class="bg-gray-900 border border-gray-800 p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-2xl font-mono text-sm">
            <div class="flex gap-2 mb-6">
              <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-red-500"></div>
              <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-yellow-500"></div>
              <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-green-500"></div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-blue-400">// MISSION CRITICAL METRICS</p>
            <p class="text-white mt-2">Scale Factor: <span class="text-green-400">10x Production Increase</span></p>
            <p class="text-white">Lead Time: <span class="text-green-400">92% Reduction</span></p>
            <p class="text-white">Contract Support: <span class="text-green-400">$100B+ Portfolio</span></p>
            <p class="text-white">System Uptime: <span class="text-green-400">99.99% (Personal Lab)</span></p>
            <div class="mt-6 p-4 bg-black/50 rounded-lg border border-gray-700">
              <p class="text-gray-500">Active Node: Liverpool_Site_Beta</p>
              <p class="text-gray-500">Security Layer: OPNsense + ZeroTrust</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="infrastructure" class="py-24 bg-gray-900/30">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-16">Platform Engineering & Networking</h2>
        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <div class="bg-gray-900 p-8 rounded-3xl border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-500/50 transition-all">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Compute & Virtualization</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 mb-6">Architecting high-availability clusters for industrial and edge applications.</p>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-gray-300">
              <li class="flex items-center"><span class="text-blue-500 mr-2">/</span> Proxmox Hypervisor Clustering</li>
              <li class="flex items-center"><span class="text-blue-500 mr-2">/</span> LXC/Docker Orchestration</li>
              <li class="flex items-center"><span class="text-blue-500 mr-2">/</span> Git-Ops Deployment Pipelines</li>
              <li class="flex items-center"><span class="text-blue-500 mr-2">/</span> ZFS Storage Management</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-900 p-8 rounded-3xl border border-gray-800 hover:border-teal-500/50 transition-all">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Security & SDN</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 mb-6">Designing zero-trust network environments with multi-layer segmentation.</p>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-gray-300">
              <li class="flex items-center"><span class="text-teal-500 mr-2">/</span> OPNsense/pfSense Architect</li>
              <li class="flex items-center"><span class="text-teal-500 mr-2">/</span> VLAN & Sublan Segmentation</li>
              <li class="flex items-center"><span class="text-teal-500 mr-2">/</span> Wireguard Tunneling</li>
              <li class="flex items-center"><span class="text-teal-500 mr-2">/</span> Automated TLS/SSL Termination</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-900 p-8 rounded-3xl border border-gray-800 hover:border-purple-500/50 transition-all">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Edge Intelligence</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 mb-6">Local-first AI deployment for autonomous decision making and HMI.</p>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-gray-300">
              <li class="flex items-center"><span class="text-purple-500 mr-2">/</span> Ollama (Offline LLM) Inference</li>
              <li class="flex items-center"><span class="text-purple-500 mr-2">/</span> PyTorch Computer Vision</li>
              <li class="flex items-center"><span class="text-purple-500 mr-2">/</span> Custom HMI/Dashboard Design</li>
              <li class="flex items-center"><span class="text-purple-500 mr-2">/</span> MQTT/REST IoT Pipelines</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="industrial" class="py-24 px-6 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-16 items-start">
        <div class="flex-1">
          <h2 class="text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-8">Industrial Impact</h2>
          <div class="space-y-12">
            <div>
              <h4 class="text-blue-400 font-mono text-sm mb-2 uppercase tracking-widest">Case Study: Lockheed Martin</h4>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">The TPY Scale-Up (10x Output)</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-400 mt-4 leading-relaxed">
                By redesigning the flow-line architecture and integrating automated torque/tooling metrics, I successfully reduced the lead time for the TPY program from **2 years down to 2 months**.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="text-teal-400 font-mono text-sm mb-2 uppercase tracking-widest">Strategic Value: Contract Acquisition</h4>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">12-Figure Proposal Engineering</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-400 mt-4 leading-relaxed">
                Provided the technical and manufacturing architecture "Proof of Concept" for multiple 12-figure defense contracts, bridging the gap between sales promises and engineering reality.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex-1 w-full bg-black/60 rounded-3xl p-8 border border-gray-800">
           
           <p class="text-center text-xs text-gray-500 mt-4 font-mono">Figure 1.2: Standardized Secure IIoT Deployment Pattern</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="research" class="py-24 bg-gradient-to-b from-gray-900 to-black">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-16 text-center">Active R&D: The Autonomy Lab</h2>
        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
          <div class="order-2 lg:order-1">
             <div class="bg-[#050505] p-6 rounded-2xl border border-blue-500/20 shadow-2xl">
               <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4 border-b border-gray-800 pb-4">
                 <span class="text-white font-bold">Lab Status: Mobile_Node_01</span>
                 <span class="flex items-center text-green-500 text-xs"><span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-green-500 mr-2 animate-pulse"></span> SYSTEM NOMINAL</span>
               </div>
               <div class="space-y-4 font-mono text-xs">
                 <p class="text-blue-400">> Initializing 48V Power Telemetry... <span class="text-white">[OK]</span></p>
                 <p class="text-blue-400">> Mounting ZFS Pool (48TB RaidZ2)... <span class="text-white">[OK]</span></p>
                 <p class="text-blue-400">> Loading Local LLM (Llama 3)... <span class="text-white">[OK]</span></p>
                 <p class="text-blue-400">> Establishing Wireguard SDN... <span class="text-white">[OK]</span></p>
                 <p class="text-white mt-4 border-t border-gray-800 pt-4">Target: Offline-First Human Autonomy</p>
               </div>
             </div>
          </div>
          <div class="order-1 lg:order-2">
            <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6">The 39' Mobile HomeLab</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 mb-6 text-lg">
              This isn't a hobby; it's an infrastructure testing ground. I'm converting a bus into a self-sustaining, AI-integrated node that features:
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-4">
              <li class="flex gap-4">
                <span class="bg-gray-800 p-3 rounded-lg text-blue-400 text-xl">üîã</span>
                <div>
                  <h5 class="text-white font-bold">Microgrid Intelligence</h5>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Real-time solar/battery telemetry via ESP32 and MQTT.</p>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-4">
                <span class="bg-gray-800 p-3 rounded-lg text-teal-400 text-xl">üõ∞Ô∏è</span>
                <div>
                  <h5 class="text-white font-bold">Decentralized Networking</h5>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Zero-Trust remote access and site-to-site failover.</p>
                </div>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <footer id="contact" class="py-24 border-t border-gray-800 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-8">Architecting the future of systems.</h2>
      <div class="flex justify-center gap-8 mb-12">
        <a href="mailto:schauer.mitchell@gmail.com" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white transition-colors">Email</a>
        <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/mitchell-schauer" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white transition-colors">LinkedIn</a>
        <a href="https://github.com/mitchschauer" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white transition-colors">GitHub</a>
      </div>
      <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">¬© 2026 Mitchell Schauer | Designed for Decentralization & Resilience</p>
    </footer>
  </main>
</Layout>